{"tid":1842746,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[你放返垃圾筒先講啦]黨鐵加強防疫工作　每兩小時清潔消毒車站","createTime":"2020-01-26T01:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T01:49:24.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7e3c990b02d8c72958c961fd8fe9769e08643637","tid":1842746,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:20:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你放返垃圾筒先講啦黨鐵</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200126/s00001/1579996800831/%e3%80%90%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e5%8a%a0%e5%bc%b7%e9%98%b2%e7%96%ab%e5%b7%a5%e4%bd%9c-%e6%af%8f%e5%85%a9%e5%b0%8f%e6%99%82%e6%b8%85%e6%bd%94%e6%b6%88%e6%af%92%e8%bb%8a%e7%ab%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200126%2Fs00001%2F1579996800831%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%25bc%25b7%25e9%2598%25b2%25e7%2596%25ab%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e4%25bd%259c-%25e6%25af%258f%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b0%258f%25e6%2599%2582%25e6%25b8%2585%25e6%25bd%2594%25e6%25b6%2588%25e6%25af%2592%25e8%25bb%258a%25e7%25ab%2599&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJXejezXkYyU2Z26LisGJHUw%3D&h=98086d54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200126%2Fs00001%2F1579996800831%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%25ad%25a6%25e6%25bc%25a2%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25b8%25af%25e9%2590%25b5%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%25bc%25b7%25e9%2598%25b2%25e7%2596%25ab%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e4%25bd%259c-%25e6%25af%258f%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b0%258f%25e6%2599%2582%25e6%25b8%2585%25e6%25bd%2594%25e6%25b6%2588%25e6%25af%2592%25e8%25bb%258a%25e7%25ab%2599&h=e4c1ea57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200126/s00001/1579996800831/%e3%80%90%e6%ad%a6%e6%bc%a2%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e6%b8%af%e9%90%b5%e5%8a%a0%e5%bc%b7%e9%98%b2%e7%96%ab%e5%b7%a5%e4%bd%9c-%e6%af%8f%e5%85%a9%e5%b0%8f%e6%99%82%e6%b8%85%e6%bd%94%e6%b6%88%e6%af%92%e8%bb%8a%e7%ab%99</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，因應新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情，為保障乘客健康，昨日（25日）起加強防疫工作，包括增加鐵路車站及車廂的清潔，各車站的清潔消毒工作，會加密至每兩小時一次，並會以1比99漂白水清潔站內乘客經常接觸到的地方，例如扶手電梯、升降機，售票機等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，西九龍站、羅湖站、落馬洲站、紅磡站及機場站，港鐵均以1比49漂白水清潔車站，全線本地93個車站的空調系統的隔塵網會加密更換及清洗；車站將加強抽入新鮮空氣，令空氣流通。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，已要求全線車站員工當值期間佩戴口罩，每天上班前亦需量度體溫。其轄下管理的物業設施，所有管理處與保安部員工、清潔工人及各承辦商均已接獲指示，需要在當值時佩戴口罩及每天上班前量度體溫。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵會透過車站的乘客資料顯示屏，宣傳提醒乘客預防新型冠狀病毒肺炎及保持良好衛生習慣的信息，亦提醒任何旅客如感到不適，應盡早求診。"},{"pid":"83d4a4f3eede50b5a5e6876b56274749306bd3d4","tid":1842746,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:47:19.000Z","msg":"黑警死坐家"},{"pid":"77a9c0f1391ea9ac384faacbfe58412ad570a33f","tid":1842746,"uid":345819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:49:24.000Z","msg":"元朗站都要1:49啦住埋咁多鄉黑全港最低賤階層"}]}